UMnuz Mthokozisi Mnyandu waseWyebank, usolwa ngokuthumba, ukudlwengula nokubamba inkunzi ehlomile abesifazane abayisishagalombili ezindaweni ezehlukene okubalwa kuzo eNanda, KwaNdengezi nasePinetown. Abanye balaba besifazane kuvele ukuthi wayebabamba bezihambela bese enza sengathi uyabashela bese eyabathumba ayobadlwengula. Kuvele ukuthi uma benqaba wayebashaya ngezimpama abakhombe nangommese. IJaji uMadam Justice Masipi uthe uMnyandu uwaphikile wonke amacala athweswe wona. Uveze ukuthi laba besifazane abebathumba ebadlwengule bonke babeneminyaka engu-16 abanye beneminyaka engaphansi kwalokhu futhi abanye beseyizintombi nto, bengakaze bazibandakanye ngokocansi. Kuvele ukuthi ummangalelwa ubedlwengula abagilwa ngaphandle kwekhondomu. Kwesinye isehlo, kuthiwa umgilwa wadlwengulwa ummangalelwa nabanye abangani bakhe ababili beshintshana ngaye. Enkantolo kuvele ukuthi ummangalelwa uthi wayethandana nabagilwa futhi babevumelene ngokuthi baye ocansini. Uveze enkantolo ukuthi ulale nabesifazane abaningi kangaka ngoba akakwazi ukulala nomuntu wesifazane kabili.